textDisplay:
@kuzz1191 Even if you prefer him for the role, obviously they chose Depp for a reason, and it's a pretty crappy and unfair reason for the continuity break.

Fwiw  I thought depp played grindelwald well,  but would have been happy with Mads from the start.  You guys are right that he looks a more grounded version of the character, but deeps version wasn't out of line with the tone of the movies at all.

I just hate to see anybody screwed over like this.  Wrong is wrong, and if anything similar happened to me or a loved one, I would hope people would speak up and make things right.

